data.description: WELCOMING 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom, 2 Car Garage Pool home with Family room, located in desirable Deep Creek. LOW HOA FEES & NO FLOOD REQUIRED!! CLICK ON THE VIRTUAL TOUR LINK 1 FOR THE VIDEO AND VIRTUAL LINK 2 FOR THE 3D TOUR. The lovely home features a bright and airy floor plan, vaulted ceilings, tile flooring in main living areas, and MUCH MORE! This home is great for entertaining with a spacious living room that flows to the kitchen.  The kitchen offers ALL white appliances, granite countertops, closet pantry, and breakfast bar. The family room off the kitchen expands your entertaining space. The master bedroom has a glass slider for pool access, two walk-in closets, and a private bathroom with single vanity with storage, ALL tile walk-in shower, soaking tub, and linen closet. The guest bedrooms are a good size with walk-in closets and on a split floor plan providing plenty of privacy.  The nearby guest bathroom has an ALL-tile walk-in shower and door for lanai access. Step out to your spacious lanai where you can sip your morning coffee or an evening beverage as you enjoy the BEAUTIFUL Florida weather, take a refreshing dip in your private heated pool or unwind in the spa, with solar and electric heating for you to enjoy both year round!2023 ROOF - 2023 LANAI SCREENING - SCREENED GARAGE DOOR. Deep Creek Golf Course is just a couple of miles down the road and a short car ride to world-class beaches. Easy access to local favorites such as Fishermen’ s Village, Ponce De Leon Park, shopping & boutiques, fine & casual dining, and LIVE entertainment. Schedule your showing TODAY!
